Description:
    Installs ActionText with Tailwind CSS integration.
    This command is redirected to our custom generator.

Example:
    bin/rails generate action_text:install

    This will:
        - Redirect to `rails generate action_text`
        - Install ActionText with Tailwind CSS styling
        - Create migration for ActionText tables
        - Install Trix editor with TypeScript support
        - Create Stimulus controller for Trix editor

